==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Purchaser
<hw>Pur"chas*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who purchases; one who acquires property for a consideration, generally
of money; a buyer; a vendee.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>One who acquires an estate in lands
by his own act or agreement, or who takes or obtains an estate by any
means other than by descent or inheritance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Purdah</ent>⟦br⟧
